  <brief_title>Effect Of Biomechanical Stimulation On Skeletal Health In Adolescent And Young Women With Anorexia Nervosa</brief_title>
  <official_title>EFFECT OF BIOMECHANICAL STIMULATION ON SKELETAL HEALTH IN ADOLESCENT AND YOUNG WOMEN WITH ANOREXIA NERVOSA</official_title>
